{"tid":1665143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"竟然冇人知Pacific Coffee係支那公司 !!!","createTime":"2019-10-20T12:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T13:27:50.000Z","uid":262529,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03e2db23fd5d996776750d761b872b65474c1d91","tid":1665143,"uid":262529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"今日見到手足門裝修左好多中資公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係咁耐以黎竟然一間Pacific Coffee都冇比人裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家只要google下就知道其實Pacific Coffee係2010已經賣左八成股份比華潤創業<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>華潤集團係支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以Pacific Coffee已經係支那公司</strong></span><br />\n大家記住唔好幫Pacific Coffee裝修啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPacific Coffee簡史<br />\n1992年，Thomas Neir創立太平洋咖啡。第一所咖啡店設於香港中環的美國銀行中心。<br />\n2005年4月6日，其士國際集團旗下上市公司其士科技(於2007年更名「其士泛亞」)以2.05億港元收購太平洋咖啡。<br />\n2008-09年度錄得稅後虧損2,030萬港元。<br />\n2009年7月，太平洋咖啡於澳門中區新馬路中央廣場試業，於澳門開設首家分店。<br />\n2009-10年度錄得稅後盈利1,760萬港元。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2010年6月29日，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">華潤創業以3.266億港元(4,187.2萬美元)，向其士泛亞收購香港太平洋咖啡八成股份，為集團打開內地的咖啡店市場作好準備</span></span>。而其士泛亞將繼續保留太平洋咖啡兩成的權益。而品牌的主調顏色調整為鮮明的紅、黑、白，＂Company＂一字也從商標上被刪除。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n2015年，其商標正式全面更新為紅圈與咖啡杯及咖啡豆圖案的組合，紅圈內取而代之的是 「Pacific Coffee」。Pacific Coffee提供的不僅僅是一杯完美的咖啡，而是一種更豐富的生活方式。「一杯一念一世界」 成為 Pacific Coffee新的使命。"},{"pid":"a06ff25cd812c2c308674bcb5d20d3473d3dcc82","tid":1665143,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"樓主呢2個月訓撚左"},{"pid":"d2e06316b57d3c875d1d59af74a1019689f4e5c4","tid":1665143,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話Pacific係裝飾咩？<br />\n未重到要裝修"},{"pid":"25aae4d800554d18c9a2f44befb3c64e8d371365","tid":1665143,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"樓主真係on9冇藥醫"},{"pid":"cdb4179659fef041657b9484856687623e63cb70","tid":1665143,"uid":262529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06ff25cd812c2c308674bcb5d20d3473d3dcc82","tid":1665143,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"樓主呢2個月訓撚左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"我只係見到小米唔係國企都燒左先開post姐"},{"pid":"9c771bbf2310a56ce081227f7b5179f97865b17d","tid":1665143,"uid":262529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2e06316b57d3c875d1d59af74a1019689f4e5c4","tid":1665143,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話Pacific係裝飾咩？<br />\n未重到要裝修"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"但連裝飾都冇見過"}]}